# =============================================================================
# ⚠️  CRITICAL: October 2025 API Implementation Files - Extra Review Required
# =============================================================================
# These files contain October 2025 API implementations (GPT-5, Claude 4.5,
# Gemini 2.5) that AI agents with outdated training data may incorrectly "fix"
# to older API versions. Require explicit approval before merging changes.
#
# If an AI agent modifies these files, VERIFY the changes are correct by:
# 1. Running: python validate_api_versions.py
# 2. Reading: docs/AI_AGENT_GUIDELINES.md
# 3. Checking commit message explains WHY the change is needed
#
# DO NOT approve changes that:
# - Change GPT-5 models to GPT-4 models
# - Change "max_output_tokens" to "max_tokens" for GPT-5
# - Change "text.format" to "response_format" for GPT-5
# - Change "/v1/responses" to "/v1/chat/completions" for GPT-5
# - Change TTS model to anything other than tts-1/tts-1-hd (OpenAI)
# =============================================================================

